values: Two days in a row writing in live journal; wow! I already feel like one of the gang.  Unfortunately, I don't have much to share right now, but you'll be hearing from me.  I know you'll be patiently waiting.
This is the first time I've ever written in live journal and I must admit, it's pretty thrilling.  I just wanted to say hello to Little Billy!
